    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Create a UGC-style video prompt using both the reference image and the user description.\n\n**Inputs**\n- User description: `{{ $('Video Idea Form').item.json['Description'] }}`\n- Reference image analysis: `{{ $('Analyze Reference Image').item.json.text }}`\n\n**Rules**\n- Keep the style casual, authentic, and realistic.\n- Default model: veo3_fast\n- Output only one JSON object with the key: video_prompt.\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=## SYSTEM PROMPT: Structured Video Ad Prompt Generator\n\nGenerate a structured video ad prompt strictly based on the master schema: {{ $json.json_master }}\n\nThe final result must be a JSON object with exactly two top-level keys: `title` and `final_prompt`.\n\nConstraints:\n- The output must be valid JSON.\n- `title`: short, descriptive, unique (max 15 words).\n- `final_prompt`: a single-line JSON string following the exact structure of the master schema.\n- No explanations, markdown, or extra text.\n- Escape all inner quotes in the `final_prompt` string.\n\nExpected output format:\n{\n  \"title\": \"A unique short title for the scene\",\n  \"final_prompt\": \"{...stringified JSON of the full prompt...}\"\n}"
        }
      },
      "id": "n13",
      "name": "AI Agent: Generate Video Script",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1992,
        480
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const structuredPrompt = $input.first().json.output.final_prompt;\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    prompt: JSON.stringify(structuredPrompt),\n    model: \"veo3_fast\",\n    aspectRatio: \"16:9\"\n  }\n};\n"
      },
      "id": "n14",
      "name": "Format Prompt",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        2400,
        480
      ]
    },
